DTSTAMP:20260503T024732Z
UID:30ed1390-7c23-433e-87a1-b88b82c9d50f
DTSTART:20260817T120000
DTEND:20260822T210000
DESCRIPTION:Your woodworking journey starts here\, with this 6-day intensiv
 e class.  Intro to Woodworking is designed for beginners interested the fu
 ndamentals of woodworking\, focusing on machine techniques.  No prior expe
 rience is required. With a maximum of 8 students\, you'll receive personal
 ized instruction in a fully equipped machine room. By the end of this clas
 s\, you will have the ability to tackle more woodworking projects on your 
 own.
SUMMARY:Intro to Woodworking
URL;VALUE=URI:https://ce.sbwi.edu/s/courseoffering/0P0Hu000000TbwhKAC
END:VEVENT
